article.headline: Jarod Lucas' 30 points leads Nevada over Portland 108-83
article.description: — Jarod Lucas' 30 points led Nevada over Portland 108-83 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Jarod Lucas' 30 points leads Nevada over Portland 108-83
article.story: RENO, Nev. -- — Jarod Lucas' 30 points led Nevada over Portland 108-83 on Saturday night. Lucas shot 9 for 14 (6 for 8 from 3-point range) and 6 of 6 from the free-throw line for the Wolf Pack (4-0). Tre Coleman scored 15 points, going 4 of 6 from the floor, including 2 for 4 from 3-point range, and 5 for 5 from the line. Tyler Harris led the Pilots (3-2) in scoring, finishing with 19 points and seven rebounds. Vasilije Vucinic added 17 points for Portland. In addition, Juan Sebastian Gorosito had 15 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
